CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784648895
OL,3,CRNLI urge beach-goers to stay safe as
OL,4,Ctwo-metre swell expected
OL,6,FRNLI lifeguards say a two-metre swell
OL,7,Fis forecast over the weekend (18 and
OL,8,F19 July) at Coldingham Bay in the
OL,9,FScottish Borders.
OL,11,FThe team has issued a safety warning,
OL,12,Freminding visitors how to stay safe
OL,13,Fwhilst at the beach.
OL,15,FLifeguards are currently present at
OL,16,FColdingham Bay during the hours of
OL,17,F10am-6pm. It's one of the few beaches
OL,18,Fin Scotland with lifeguards and
OL,19,Fthey're asking beach users to respect
OL,20,Fthe area flags and ask for advice from
OL,21,Fthemselves if needed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
