PN,32502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784648895
OL,3,CRNLI urge beach-goers to stay safe as
OL,4,Ctwo-metre swell expected
OL,6,FSenior Lifeguard Rose said: "Whilst
OL,7,Fthe warm weather may not be focused on
OL,8,Fthe south-east coast of Scotland, it
OL,9,Fis still due to be warm, with the surf
OL,10,Fforecast suggesting a short-lived
OL,11,Fswell building from Friday, peaking on
OL,12,FSunday.
OL,14,F"If you're headed to the coast, you
OL,15,Fshould always try to visit a
OL,16,Flifeguarded beach. The lifeguards will
OL,17,Fset up safe zones for different water
OL,18,Fsports.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784648895
OL,3,CRNLI urge beach-goers to stay safe as
OL,4,Ctwo-metre swell expected
OL,6,F"Always swim or bodyboard between the
OL,7,Fred and yellow flags. There may be
OL,8,Fblack and white flags which are for
OL,9,Fsurfers, paddle boarders and kayaks or
OL,10,Fother hard craft. These water users
OL,11,Fshould stay out of the red and yellow
OL,12,Fflag zone.
OL,14,F'When the red flag is flying, please
OL,15,Fdo not enter the water as the
OL,16,Flifeguards have decided the conditions
OL,17,Fare too dangerous.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1784648895
OL,3,CRNLI urge beach-goers to stay safe as
OL,4,Ctwo-metre swell expected
OL,6,F"If there are breaking waves, stay
OL,7,Fwithin your depth and be aware of how
OL,8,Fyou are drifting with the currents. If
OL,9,Fyou find yourself in a current, don't
OL,10,Fpanic. Try to stand up and wade back
OL,11,Fto shore.
OL,13,F"If you're out of your depth, or need
OL,14,Fhelp, keep hold of your board or float
OL,15,Fon your back with your ears submerged,
OL,16,Fraise a hand and shout for help; a
OL,17,Flifeguard will come to you."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
